messages.messageBody:
The PhoenixUnschoolers list isn't owned by anyone (the originator left town
and no one had the ability to keep it up...no passwords etc.) and that list
is just an open blank at the moment, as far as I know.

The Phoenix_Unschoolers@yahoogroups.com is active, moderated and owned.

Jacki in Chandler who would be happy to give your friend in Tempe a holler

We have finally, if temporarily, moved to Phoenix! If you have not
received my new contact info from another mailing, and would like to
have it, please send me a note offlist.

We will be seeking a community of homeschoolers and those with similar
natural and conscious lifestyles. If you or your friends live in the
Phoenix area and would like to make a connection, please let me know
offlist.

Sandra Kee
Anne Elizabeth (8), Olivia (7), and husband Thom
